  - var shuttleIcon = '<span class="glyphicon glyphicon-flag"></span> '
  - var shuttleService = shuttleIcon + 'Shuttle service'
  #hotels.container
    include layouts/hotels
    
  #shuttle.container
    h2 Shuttle Service
    .row
      .col-sm-6
        p
          | Parking is limited near the ceremony venue. 
        p
          | Therefore, we ask that guests who are able please park in the parking area noted above 
          | (Faith Lutheran Church). 
        p
          | Designated vehicles will be available to transport guests between the parking area and the ceremony venue. 
        p
          | After the ceremony, these vehicles will be available to bring guests back to the parking area.
        p
          | There will be priority parking available at each venue for those with mobility concerns or other special requirements.
      .col-sm-6
        p
          | If you are staying at one of the hotels listed above as offering shuttle service (marked with the !{shuttleIcon} icon), 
          | we will provide a shuttle to all venues throughout the day. 
        p
          | All guests staying in Willmar hotels and wishing to use the shuttle will need to gather in front of the lobby of the Best Western Plus.
        p
          | The shuttle will leave the Best Western Plus in Willmar at 1:25pm, 
          | and head to the Northern Inn & Suites to pick up guests there.
        p
          | The shuttle will depart the Northern Inn & Suites at 1:45pm. 
          | After the ceremony, the shuttle will bring guests to the reception venue.
        p
          | Throughout the evening, the shuttle will make rounds between the reception venue, 
          | select hotels in Willmar (!{shuttleIcon}), 
          | and the Northern Inn &amp Suites in Spicer. 
  
